# The api image only needs the api/ package and requirements.txt.
# Ignore everything, then re-include just those — keeps the build context
# tiny regardless of how large datasets/goes_cache/crops grow on the server.
*
!api/
!requirements.txt
# labeling-tool image (Dockerfile.labeling) shares this build context and
# COPYs these two — without re-including them they're stripped and COPY fails.
!labeling_tool.py
!auto_classify.py
